 download and fill out the new registration form from MCS website.\r\n\r\nLast week our students competed in the Inter-School Chinese Speech Contest hosted by Ann Arbor Chinese School. We are very proud of the performance of all our students. Congratulate to the following winners from our school:\r\n\r\n演講比賽：\r\n\r\n[第一組] 第一名江秉陽；第二名盛嘉詰；第三名鄭羽翔。\r\n\r\n[第二組] 第一名魏郁安\r\n\r\n[第三組] 第一名王淨慧\r\n\r\n看圖說故事比賽：\r\n\r\n[第七組]          第二名    陳楷文,王淨德,鄺紹耘；\r\n\r\n[第八組]          第三名：鄒佩成,呂詠恩,邱 晧。\r\n\r\nFor students who didn\'t win, don\'t be discouraged. There are always opportunities in the future. Attached is a news release issued by AnnArbor Chinese School. Thanks to our ex-principal Lisa Hou, she took some pictures during the contest and we will post them on our website. We also want to thank our 教務主任 羅庭偉, who spent a lot of time coordinating the whole speech constest event. We also want to thank teachers who took their personal time to train these students before the competition:    There are some new community information posted on our website. You may find it interesteing to you. From time to time we will post photos and articles to share with you. So don\'t forget to visit MCS website.   -\r\n\r\n-- Hunan-Hunan will deliver your food orders this week.\r\n\r\n--- Eric Wu\'s tennis class continues at schoolcraft college tennis court afterschool.\r\n\r\n--- Parents on duty: 劉蔚芝, 徐劼池\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://michiganchineseschool.org/blog/wp-content/uploads/2010/05/A十七屆密西根州中文學校校際演講比賽.pdf\">A十七屆密西根州中文學校校際演講比賽</a>\r\n\r\nBest Regards\r\n\r\nAlex Tang Principal, MCS','MCS Communication - 5/22/2010',0,'','publish','closed','open','','mcs-communication-5222010','','','2010-05-21 15:02:42','2010-05-21 19:02:42','',0,'http://michiganchineseschool.org/blog/?p=76',0,'post','',0),(77,1,'2010-05-21 15:01:17','2010-05-21 19:01:17','','A十七屆密西根州中文學校校際演講比賽',0,'','inherit','open','open','','a%e5%8d%81%e4%b8%83%e5%b1%86%e5%af%86%e8%a5%bf%e6%a0%b9%e5%b7%9e%e4%b8%ad%e6%96%87%e5%ad%b8%e6%a0%a1%e6%a0%